long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quick Shortcut is a powerful Chrome extension designed to streamline your browsing experience by allowing you to effortlessly redirect URLs. Whether you want to reroute specific Salesforce pages like changeSet,Workflow rule, Process builder, dev console etc , manage URL patterns, Quick Shortcut also provides a user-friendly interface to customize your browsing behavior to suit your needs as well as add favourite options for productivity.
